name: Travel the world
description: That is why you fail.

name: Walk on the moon
description: Through the Force, things you will see. Other places. The future - the past. Old friends long gone.

name: Find your soulmate
description: Do. Or do not. There is no try.

name: Buy an island
description: Reckless he is. Matters are worse.

name: Bottle of joy
description: Hmm. In the end, cowards are those who follow the dark side.

name: Botte of love
description: Difficult to see. Always in motion is the future...

name: Bottle of strength
description: Soon will I rest, yes, forever sleep. Earned it I have. Twilight is upon me, soon night must fall.

name: Bottle of calm
description: Adventure. Excitement. A Jedi craves not these things.

name: Bottle of courage
description: Mudhole? Slimy? My home this is!

name: Bottle of motivation
description: Once you start down the dark path, forever will it dominate your destiny, consume you it will.

name: Bottle of rage
description: Clear your mind must be, if you are to find the villains behind this plot.

name: Bottle of envy
description: Like fire across the galaxy the Clone Wars spread. In league with the wicked Count Dooku, more and more planets slip. Against this threat, upon the Jedi Knights falls the duty to lead the newly formed army of the Republic. And as the heat of war grows, so, to, grows the prowess of one most gifted student of the Force.

name: Fly
description: Always two there are, no more, no less. A master and an apprentice.

name: Teleport
description: Already know you that which you need.

name: Talk to animals
description: Truly wonderful, the mind of a child is.

name: Be invisible
description: Luminous beings are we - not this crude matter.

name: Jump to your career
description: Pain, suffering, death I feel. Something terrible has happened. Young Skywalker is in pain. Terrible pain

name: Learn a new language
description: To answer power with power, the Jedi way this is not. In this war, a danger there is, of losing who we are.

name: Bottle of edge case brainstorms
description: Your weapons, you will not need them.

name: Early retirement
description: Good relations with the Wookiees, I have.
